---
import '../styles/static-pages.styles.scss';
import FeedbackForm from '../components/layout/feedback-form';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const pageTitle = "Write for Us at Triplay.ai: Join Our Contributor Community";
const description = 'Contribute to Triplay.ai: We seek passionate travelers. Write for us and share your adventures with a global audience.';
const openGraph = {
	basic: {
		title: "Write for Us at Triplay.ai: Join Our Contributor Community",
		description: 'Contribute to Triplay.ai: We seek passionate travelers. Write for us and share your adventures with a global audience.',
		type: "website",
		image: "https://triplay.ai/triplay-logo.svg",
		url: 'https://triplay.ai/write-for-us',
	}
};
---
<script>
	const handleClick = () => {
	  const form = document.getElementById('feedbackForm');
		window.scrollTo({
			top: form?.offsetTop ? form?.offsetTop - 70 : 0,
			behavior: 'smooth'
		})
	}
	document.querySelector('.to-form').addEventListener('click', () => {
		handleClick();
	});
</script>
<BaseLayout
	pageTitle={pageTitle}
	metaTitle={pageTitle}
	description={description}
	metaDescription={description}
	openGraph={openGraph}
>
	<section id='hero' class='hero'>
		<div class='row'>
			<div class='col'>
				<div class='hero__content'>
					<h1 class='hero__title'>
						Write for us
					</h1>
					<p class='hero__description'>
						Are you an avid traveller whose stories take readers to the far corners of the globe? Triplay is the
						perfect place for travellers and bloggers to create unique content and share it with like-minded
						people.</p>
					<div class='hero__buttons'>
						<div
							class='tp-button-filled to-form'
							id='contactUs'
							rel='nofollow'
							style={ { padding: '0.5rem 1rem', textDecoration: 'none' } }
						>
							Contact us
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<div class='static-page'>
		<div class='static-content'>
			<section>
				<h2>Why Collaborate with Triplay?</h2>
				<p>Triplay is not just a platform; it&apos;s a gateway to sharing your travel experiences with a burgeoning
					audience who share your zeal for exploration. Writing with us offers you:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Exposure: Your voice and vision can reach a global audience, eager to consume authentic travel stories
						and advice.
					</li>
					<li>Credibility: Build your personal or company brand by aligning with Triplay.ai, a hub for top-notch
						travel planning powered by playful AI.
					</li>
					<li>Engagement: Gain insightful feedback, interact with readers, and become part of a community that
						values travel as much as you do.
					</li>
					<li>Links: Receive a shout-out with a backlink to your own blog or website, driving traffic and increasing
						visibility.
					</li>
					<li>Promotion: Enjoy the amplification of your content through our social media channels, newsletters, and
						more.
					</li>
				</ul>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2>Your Journey with Us: The Content Odyssey</h2>
				<p>Embark on an editorial journey with us through the following phases:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Pitching: Kick-start the process by getting in touch with us. Share your ideas, and letâ€™s brainstorm
						together!
					</li>
					<li>Creating: Develop your content with a minimum of 4000 words of original, engaging narrative or
						informative guides. Embed it with legal pictures and videos that enhance the storytelling.
					</li>
					<li>Polishing: After submission, your piece will undergo a quality check, ensuring it aligns with our
						values and editorial standards.
					</li>
					<li>Publishing: Upon finalizing the content, we celebrate its launch on our platform, inviting travelers
						to navigate through your experiences.
					</li>
				</ul>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2>Content Creation Guidelines</h2>
				<p>To ensure that the collaboration is fruitful and your content captivates our audience, we ask that you
					adhere to the following guidelines:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Originality: Your submission should be a treasure chest of fresh content, not previously published
						elsewhere.
					</li>
					<li>Relevance: We revel in stories and tips centered on playful and innovative travel experiences that
						resonate with our AI-driven theme.
					</li>
					<li>Quality: Your content must be well-researched, eloquently written, and reflect a high standard of
						grammatical precision.
					</li>
					<li>Visuals: Accompany your articles with high-quality, copyright-cleared images or videos. We appreciate
						a photo story that can speak as powerfully as the written word.
					</li>
					<li>SEO Optimization: Craft your article with SEO in mind. This includes using relevant keywords, meta
						descriptions, and following best online readability practices.
					</li>
					<li>Bio & Links: Introduce yourself with a brief bio and include links to your website or social media
						profiles.
					</li>
					<li>Non-promotional: Content should be informative and engaging, not overtly promotional, except in the
						case of sponsored posts.
					</li>
				</ul>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2>Content Ideas We Love</h2>
				<p>To ensure that the collaboration is fruitful and your content captivates our audience, we ask that you
					adhere to the following guidelines:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>In-depth travel itineraries powered by AI suggestions</li>
					<li>Articles on the intersection of technology and travel</li>
					<li>Unique travel experiences and how AI can enhance them</li>
					<li>Cultural explorations and insights into global traditions</li>
					<li>Sustainable travel initiatives and eco-friendly planning</li>
					<li>Guides for digital nomads and remote work travel</li>
				</ul>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2>Sponsored Opportunities</h2>
				<p>For companies wishing to feature sponsored content on Triplay, we offer tailored packages that include
					no-follow links and wide-reaching promotional efforts across our digital presence. Reach out to us to
					discuss rates and opportunities.</p>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2>Ready to Share Your Voyage?</h2>
				<p>If Triplay sounds like the perfect home for your travel narratives or promotional content, we&apos;re
					excited
					to hear from you. Send us an email with your proposed topics and a brief abstract of your article.
					Let&apos;s
					embark on this collaborative journey and bring inspiring travel content to life, together!</p>
			</section>

		</div>
		<div id='feedbackForm' class='container static-content__container'>
			<FeedbackForm client:idle />
		</div>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>
